creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the official Hopewell Baptist Church app!

With our app, you'll have direct access to sermons from Dr. Lee Pigg, take notes on your device during service, stay in touch with our current events, and receive time sensitive information. Don't worry, we promise not to overload you with push notifications.

For more information about Hopewell, please visit: http://www.whatasavior.com/

The Hopewell Baptist App was created with the Subsplash App Platform.
descriptionShort: Hopewell Baptist Church - Leading people to follow Christ.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.
